Average allelic richness (corrected for sample size by rarefaction) per locality was calculated in the HIERFSTAT package [
44
] for R (http://www.R-project.org/). Observed and expected heterozygosity were calculated using Arlequin v3.5.1.3 [
45
]. Weir and Cockerham’s [
46
